        {
            "title": "歐洲股市收漲 媒體和電信板塊領漲 賽諾菲因新藥試驗結果不佳而大跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mPgQzYm2Ock2Y4fKQUrF.w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f2a07b289d1f6d6c3c13d527b255631f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 周四歐洲股市攀升，全球債券市場重歸平靜，且投資者加大押注美國降息的力度。賽諾菲股價因藥物臨床試驗結果令人失望而下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲斯托克600指數收漲0.6%，媒體和電信類股領漲。Publicis Groupe SA股價連續第二個交易日上漲，此前執行長Arthur Sadoun在周三的會議上對下半年表達了信心。Heidelberg Materials AG和Holcim AG股價上漲，因高盛集團開始追蹤這兩家水泥企業，並給予買入評級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">旅遊休閒板塊表現尤為疲軟，Jet2 Plc盈利預警拖累易捷航空和瑞安航空等廉價航空。賽諾菲是表現最弱的個股之一，因新濕疹藥物臨床試驗結果令人失望，股價大跌8.3%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TMGmKjP9cFUJNRCU5RL_Hw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0814b902d86a653a2b642f2539b20a21\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲股市在過去兩周走低，此前該指數上月曾逼近歷史高點。財政支出擔憂攪動全球債券市場，投資者正尋求新的催化劑。彭博報導稱，若法國總理遭罷免，總統馬克龍將避免提前舉行大選，此消息令法國CAC 40指數收窄跌幅。該指數盤中一度下跌0.6%，最終收跌0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Advance on Fed Rate Cut Bets; Sanofi Slumps</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sagarika Jaisinghani、Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E6%94%B6%E6%BC%B2-%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%A1%8A%E9%A0%98%E6%BC%B2-%E8%B3%BD%E8%AB%BE%E8%8F%B2%E5%9B%A0%E6%96%B0%E8%97%A5%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%B3%E8%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C-161258642.html",
